Wire connection

ARDUINO		GSM		Wire Color
------------------------------
GND			GND		yellow
Pin0(RX)	TX		Grey
Pin1(TX)	RX		Brown


ARDUINO		PIR		Wire Color 
-----------------------------  
GND			GND		orange     
Pin3		Output	white	   
5V			5V		red

ARDUINO		BUZZER	
-------------------
pin12		red
pin13(GND)  black


(PIR m likha hua ni hta h pin ka nam, iske lye)
(Pir m Orange color ka do pin apne traf krna r 3 pin isme wires lgana h)
(usko apne opposite traf rkhna, fir jo sbse right m hga wo 5Vpin, bich m jo hga )
(wo output pin, left m jo hga wo GND pin)
